text: LA-21 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by the Sardar Khan Bahadur Khan of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Pallandri in Sudhanoti District of Azad Kashmir, Pakistan. Category:Sudhanoti District ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016. Category:Government of Azad Kashmir Category:Constituencies of Pakistan
title: Constituency LA-21
